{"tid":2435884,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"甲級戰犯白頭佬","createTime":"2021-03-06T15:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T03:53:46.000Z","uid":323538,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"663e013a108f7efed1821aac23dc41f4789d17ea","tid":2435884,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"街工先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTOMPxe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTOMPxe.png&h=ec07bdcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住 職工盟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【有關：吳敏兒辭任職工盟主席】<br />\n日前，我們透過吳敏兒代表律師得知，她決定辭去職工盟主席一職，只保留一般執委成員身份。這是她經過苦苦掙扎、反覆思量，與代表律師詳細商討後作出的艱難決定。我們亦透過律師向她表示，完全理解和支持她的決定。今天（3月6日）我們前往懲教所探訪吳敏兒時，正式確認了此一決定。<br />\n吳敏兒投身自主工會運動近廿載，過去一直是我們的緊密戰友，並肩打過一場又一場的硬仗，未來亦將會如此。<br />\n她在任主席期間，一直以來對工運作出各項無私的奉獻和犧牲，我們在此表示衷心感謝。縱有千言萬語，也難以表達我們感激之情。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">跟其他40多位被告人士一樣，吳敏兒現正身陷囹圄，為實踐信念而失去自由，我們必定會繼續義無反顧，全力支援吳敏兒，爭取她早日獲得釋放。</span></strong><br />\nYou will never walk alone!<br />\n香港職工會聯盟<br />\n2021年3月6日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSTQwLR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSTQwLR.png&h=4cad5523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">結論：</span></strong></span> <span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>共狗一世平安</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a5edae6e00c13203fb52cdb501d539efbb72d761","tid":2435884,"uid":244808,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"663e013a108f7efed1821aac23dc41f4789d17ea","tid":2435884,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"街工先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTOMPxe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTOMPxe.png&h=ec07bdcc&s={S